      "FLIGHT SCHEDULE\nШСА\nWEST COAST AIRLINES\nEFFECTIVE SEPTEMBER 24, 1961\nHam\nBellingham\nNORTH BEND.\nCOOS BAY\nKlamath Falls\nPORTLAND\nSun Valley\nHalley-Ketchiall\nASTORER\nОМАК\nBURLE:\nRUPERT\nKalispell\nSALEM\nMosCow.\nPULLMAN\nSTORIA-\nSEASIDE\nLOGAN\nTwin Falls\nSEATTLE\nIdaho Falls\nWCA\nOLYMPIA\n- YAKIMA\nLakeview\nSPOKANE\nWenatchee\nABERDEEN-\nHOQUIAM\nTri Cities\nMEDFORD\ngoing\nyour\nway!\nALBANY.\nCORVALLIS\nBURNS\nGreat Falls\nBEND-\nREDMOND\nBAKER\nШСА\nPort Angeles\nLEWISTON-\nCLARKSTOM\nCour d'Alena\nOAKLANT\nSalt Lake Cit\nCALGARY\nWalla Walla\nSACRAMENTO\nWCA\nWC\nШСК\nШСА\nWCA\nPendleton\nCUT BANK.\nSHELBY\nEUGENE\nPocatello\nWCA\nWICH\nWCA\nWC. WCA\nWest Coast Airlines,\nflying the fast F-27\nProp-Jet, provides\nconvenient daily\nservice to more than\n60 cities throughout\nthe great Pacific West.\nWelcome Ahoard\nWCA\n\"Fast growing with the West\"",
